snippet.title: Final Fantasy IV Advance Brachioraidos
snippet.description: This video was requested, fight against Brachioraidos who is the toughest enemy in FFIV Advance, including Zeromus EG. Kept at fastest battle speed to make up for my high level, but very doable 20 levels below at slowest speed when I did it the first time with similar tactics. And yes Edward really is a powerhouse at late levels:p.
